{"tid":1370353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日去元朗前線手足入黎睇睇","createTime":"2019-07-27T03:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T05:29:55.000Z","uid":201862,"like":33,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"53b37ff5a1225e1b2731642efc97412a7eb09d05","tid":1370353,"uid":201862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:23:00.000Z","msg":"琴晚機場丫伯單野<br />\n我諗大家都有初步了解<br />\n藍絲不斷以呢件事去攻擊我地<br />\n令一班中立 淺黃ga人轉左風軚<br />\n今日返到公司 好多同事都問發生乜事<br />\n都指責機場入面ga手足<br />\n<br />\n我明白大家都對21/7發生ga事好憤怒<br />\n但係千萬要記住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好主動入村</span></span><br />\n你地主動入村的話 即係進入私人地方<br />\n對家拎正牌驅趕<br />\n<br />\n同時亦令藍絲們有理去大做文章<br />\n令到風向一下逆轉<br />\n<br />\n亦都有好大可能性<br />\n令我地之前做ga野付諸流水<br />\n呢個局面我諗和理非同勇武ga手足都唔希望見到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以我希望前線手足盡量克制<br />\n唔好咁容易比人去挑釁</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勿分化、勿捉鬼、不篤灰、不抹黑、不割蓆<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"c62ae2f37f149bd6b4fec63ad64073288f6ea465","tid":1370353,"uid":201862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:23:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a053244a82bb81d3098be3b8150393a14290aef8","tid":1370353,"uid":201862,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:24:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a3f5e7a2d6d667d2688416357e5e499b2dd83bc","tid":1370353,"uid":201862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:24:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da7722bbc45e433cd396e730cd82d9669c563b7c","tid":1370353,"uid":39872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:25:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>都唔好被動入村</strong></span>"},{"pid":"5e8dbfa32bdcd567cf5e7539d138eea3f5e7a8c7","tid":1370353,"uid":201862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da7722bbc45e433cd396e730cd82d9669c563b7c","tid":1370353,"uid":39872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27